Package: DSM
Type: Package
Title: Digital soil mapping steps (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Fatemeh Hateffard, Luc Steinbuch
Maintainer: Fatemeh Hateffard <hateffard.fatemeh@science.unideb.hu>
Description: This soil mapping package involves several essential steps, including overlaying the data points, 
              running the ML model, and assessing their uncertainty. By doing these, 
              the package can capture the spatial distribution of soil properties and create a detailed map.
